### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@apiUrl = {{baseUrl}}/api

### Get all topics
GET {{apiUrl}}/topics
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get topic by ID
GET {{apiUrl}}/topics/NCPT
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get topic by ID (Not Found)
GET {{apiUrl}}/topics/XXX
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Create new topic
POST {{apiUrl}}/topics
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "macd": "AI",
  "tenCd": "Trí tuệ nhân tạo"
}

###

### Update topic
PUT {{apiUrl}}/topics/NCPT
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenCd": "Nghiên cứu phát triển (Updated)"
}

###

### Update topic (Not Found)
PUT {{apiUrl}}/topics/XXX
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenCd": "Test Update"
}

###

### Delete topic
DELETE {{apiUrl}}/topics/AI
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Delete topic (Not Found)
DELETE {{apiUrl}}/topics/XXX
Content-Type: application/json

###
